update public.lessons l set enhancements = $ench${"industryStory":"A tester needed example request bodies and varied test data for an API and asked AI to generate them — valid, invalid and edge-case payloads. It produced a useful set in seconds, all synthetic, which they then ran and verified.","davidTip":"AI quickly drafts example requests and synthetic payloads — valid, invalid and boundary. Use them to test thoroughly, but never include real customer data, and confirm the requests actually match the API contract.","miniChallenge":"Ask AI to generate three request bodies for an endpoint — one valid, one invalid, one boundary — and check each against the API's rules.","modelAnswer":"## Example — create user\nValid: full payload with a unique email. Invalid: missing required \"email\". Boundary: a name at the maximum allowed length. All synthetic; all checked against the field rules."}$ench$::jsonb
